SELECT
                number,
                l1_tx_count,
                l2_tx_count,
                timestamp,
                l2_to_l1_messages,
                bloom,
                priority_ops_onchain_data,
                used_contract_hashes,
                bootloader_code_hash,
                default_aa_code_hash,
                protocol_version,
                system_logs,
                pubdata_input,
                fee_address
            FROM
                l1_batches
            WHERE
                is_sealed
                AND number = $1

SELECT
                number,
                l1_tx_count,
                l2_tx_count,

                l2_to_l1_messages,
                bloom,
                priority_ops_onchain_data,
                used_contract_hashes,
                bootloader_code_hash,
                default_aa_code_hash,
                evm_emulator_code_hash,
                protocol_version,
                system_logs,
                pubdata_input
            FROM
                l1_batches
            WHERE
                number = $1
